<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Firstly</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Moderators</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Can close/reopen/move/edit/delete threads.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Administrators</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: Can do all the above, plus adjust the board itself, create new forums, ban/un ban posters, give people titles, etc.<br>
<br>
Kais, Gorgash/Whistler, and myself are Moderators.  Apep is an administrator.  Jaxy is an administrator and the board owner.<br>
<br>
If you feel that someone should be banned in the thread above (or for something else), e-mail Apep and/or Jaxy.  Don't start bitching at me for not doing it.  The most I can do to them is edit all their posts to say &quot;I smell like a board troll&quot;.<br>
